# Illegal: path (-F path= Syscall form) is only legal on the exit filter list.
# Grounded in libaudit.c: case AUDIT_WATCH / case AUDIT_DIR share the guard
# `if (flags != AUDIT_FILTER_EXIT) return -EAU_EXITONLY;` (audit 3bfa048).
# user list -> EAU_EXITONLY -> auditctl aborts the rule load.
-a always,user -F path=/etc/passwd -k test-path-user
